        <p>Jira issues map to branches/PRs. We review, merge, and let CI/CD take it from there—like a real entry-level DevOps flow.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Branch per feature</li>
          <li>PR reviews before merge</li>
          <li>Simple sprint board</li>
